                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050424-50-victim541 t18050424-50-viclabel286"></join>: On the 24th of April, about eight o'clock in the evening, I met the prisoner coming out of the office-door with a box, and a parcel; the parcel fell down on the ground; I stopped him, and took the box from him; I gave the box to 
               <persName id="t18050424-50-person543">
                  Edward 
                  Lee
               <interp inst="t18050424-50-person543" type="surname" value="Lee"></interp>
