               <p>Prisoner's defence. I went in about half past eight o'clock, I was never in the office before, and facing the door going in, there is a vacancy of about two yards; I saw two men go in, and I went in; the parcels were lying by the door, I fell over them; I took this box up, I did no more, and gave it to him directly.</p>
